          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Finely-chopped-ginger-and-garlic-1652090232531-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is beginning to soften, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>pollock </strong>and cook for 1-2 min</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>remaining ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong> and <strong>garam masala </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
